    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are developping Floodcore into a full game!<br>Join our discord server for updates and chat with the devs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/05520660ea132bfecca5637a16371bb6.avif?t=1759151539\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/8be5c61ddf139f4444b63ddef3b6d12a.poster.avif?t=1759151539\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/8be5c61ddf139f4444b63ddef3b6d12a.webm?t=1759151539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/8be5c61ddf139f4444b63ddef3b6d12a.mp4?t=1759151539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Floodcore is a <strong>puzzle adventure game</strong> in which you explore an ancient civilization in a flooded world, and discover a mysterious power to overcome the temple's challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a vertical slice made by <strong>5 French students</strong> within 8 months as a graduation project. You can expect <strong>15 to 30 minutes of gameplay</strong> depending on your affinity with puzzle games and your sense of spatial awareness in a 3D environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/eb654f3976d1a6e0600bebac6751a7b3.poster.avif?t=1759151539\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/eb654f3976d1a6e0600bebac6751a7b3.webm?t=1759151539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/eb654f3976d1a6e0600bebac6751a7b3.mp4?t=1759151539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your power allows you to <strong>swap</strong> positions with specific objects in the world, or swap them together. Delve further into the temple and solve puzzles that require you to become a part of them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/4109a968ece4426a5afa4a71da05c1b2.poster.avif?t=1759151539\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/4109a968ece4426a5afa4a71da05c1b2.webm?t=1759151539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/4109a968ece4426a5afa4a71da05c1b2.mp4?t=1759151539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each area expands on the swap mechanic and makes you use it in different ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some will challenge you and require you to anticipate several moves ahead, while others will need you to figure out every possibility, and there are often several different solutions for them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/546cae6c2bd5a39fbedb9b45bc94c439.poster.avif?t=1759151539\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/546cae6c2bd5a39fbedb9b45bc94c439.webm?t=1759151539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/546cae6c2bd5a39fbedb9b45bc94c439.mp4?t=1759151539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will discover multiple ruins laid by an ancient civilisation, each with its own visuals and purpose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the temple's surface to its underground, all the way to a luxuriant garden, you will experience each area differently with their puzzles and atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/6555cf0cf76c662a7bb7347ab7fd6d59.poster.avif?t=1759151539\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/6555cf0cf76c662a7bb7347ab7fd6d59.webm?t=1759151539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/6555cf0cf76c662a7bb7347ab7fd6d59.mp4?t=1759151539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At any point in time, you can take a step back and enjoy the calm atmosphere with the sound of waves, birds, wind and waterfalls.</p>",
